local Animate = require "actions/Animate" local Wait = require "actions/Wait" local Do = require "actions/Do" local Ease = require "actions/Ease"
return function(self, player, prevState) if prevState == self.STATE_IDLE then local eyes = self.scene.objectLookup.Eyes1 local arm = self.scene.objectLookup.Arm1 eyes.hidden = false eyes:run { Animate(eyes.sprite, "blink"), Animate(eyes.sprite, "forward"), Wait(1), Animate(eyes.sprite, "smile"), Do(function() arm.hidden = false arm.x = eyes.x - 60 arm.y = eyes.y end), Ease(arm, "y", function() return arm.y + 90 end, 4), Do(function() arm:updateCollision() end), Wait(2), Ease(arm, "y", function() return arm.y - 90 end, 4), Do(function() arm:updateCollision() arm.hidden = true eyes.sprite:setAnimation("forwardblink") end) } end end
return function(self) self.hidden = true if GameState:isFlagSet(self) then self:remove() end end
